Local development

# clone the repository
git clone git@github.com:gethugothemes/andromeda-light.git

# cd in the project directory
$ cd andromeda-light/exampleSite/

# Start local dev server
$ hugo server --themesDir ../..

Or Check out Full Documentation.

Content Management System

This project has been pre-configured to work with Forestry a git-based CMS, import your repository in Forestry and you will be able to edit and preview your site .

Any changes you make in Forestry will be committed back to the repo and deployed if you use Netlify.

Reporting Issues

We use GitHub Issues as the official bug tracker for the andromeda light Template. Please Search existing issues. Someone may have already reported the same problem. If your problem or idea has not been addressed yet, feel free to open a new issue.
